\f0\fs24 \cf0 README\
\
The files provided within this .zip file are meant to reproduce the tables and figures included in the article \cf2 "\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
How to Get Coal Country to Vote for Climate Policy: The Effect of a \'91Just Transition Agreement\'92 on Spanish Election Results\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 " by Diane Bolet, Fergus Green and Mikel Gonz\'e1lez-Eguino in the APSR. \
\
Figure 1 and Figure B.1 were conducted in R. The rest of the analysis is conducted using Stata 17. \
\

\f1\b Content of the files\

\f0\b0      \'93README.rtf\'94 contains the content of the files and how to replicate the Tables and Figures. 
\f1\b \
    
\f0\b0  \'93Supplemental_Material.pdf\'94 is the Online Appendix.
\f1\b \
   
\f0\b0   \'932008.dta\'94 contains relevant variables for the year 2008 to Tables, 1, 2, C.1, C.3, E.2, and E.3.\
     \'932008c.dta\'94 contains relevant variables for the year 2008 to prepare Table E.5. \
     \'932011.dta\'94 contains relevant variables for the year 2011 to prepare Tables, 1, 2, C.1, C.3, E.2, and E.3. \
     \'932015.dta\'94 contains relevant variables for the year 2015 to prepare Tables, 1, 2, C.1, C.3, E.2, and E.3.  \
     \'932015e.dta\'94 contains relevant variables for the year 2015 to prepare Table D.1.\
     \'932016_turnout_podemos.dta\'94 contains relevant variables for the year 2016 to prepare Table E.4.\
     \'932016.dta\'94 contains relevant variables for the year 2016 to prepare Tables, 1, 2, C.1, C.3, E.2, and E.3. \
     \'932016elecciones.xlsx\'94 contains relevant variables to prepare Figure 1. \
     \'932016lagged.dta\'94 contains relevant variables for the year 2016 to prepare Table E.2.\
     \'932019_turnout_podemos.dta\'94 contains relevant variables for the year 2019 to prepare Table E.4.\
     \'932019.dta\'94 contains relevant variables for the year 2019 to prepare Tables, 1, 2, C.1, C.3, E.2, and E.3. \
     \'932019elecciones.xlsx\'94 contains relevant variables to prepare Figure 1.\
     \'93age_population.dta\'94 contains relevant variables to prepare Tables, 1, 2, C.1, C.3, E.2 and E.3. \
     \'93age.dta\'94 contains the relevant variables to prepare Table D.1. \
     \'93appendix.do\'94 contains the Stata commands that allow to replicate all the findings presented in the appendix. \
     \'93articles_full.xlsx\'94 contains relevant variables to prepare Figure B.1. \
     \'93coalmines.dta\'94 contains relevant variables to prepare Figures D.1 and F.1, and Tables D.1 and F.1. \
     "codebook.xlsx" contains the variable names in the datasets that correspond to the main variables in the paper and appendix.\
     \'93distance_closure_coalmines.dta\'94 contains relevant variables to prepare Table E.5. \
     \'93education.dta\'94 contains relevant variables to prepare Tables, 1, 2, C.1, C.3, E.2. and E.3. \
     \'93education1.dta\'94 contains relevant variables to prepare Table D.1.  \
