     \'93Ethical Approval_BC3.pdf\'94 and \'93Ethical Approval_Durham.pdf\'94 are the certificates of ethical approval. \
     \'93figure_B.1.R\'94 contains the R commands that allow to replicate Figure B.1. \
     \'93figure1.R\'94 contains the R commands that allow to replicate Figure 1. \
     \'93main_analysis.do\'94 contains the Stata commands that allow to replicate all the findings presented in  the manuscript. \
     \'93miners.dta\'94 contains relevant variables to prepare Tables 2 and C.1. \
     \'93unemployment.dta\'94 contains relevant variables to prepare Table D.1.  \
