     \'93unemploymentgrowth.dta\'94 contains relevant variables to prepare Tables, 1, 2, C.1, C.3, and E.3.   \
     \'93votediff.dta\'94 contains relevant variables to prepare Figures D.1 and F.1, and Tables D.1 and F.1.\
